*.svg
*.pdf
*.docx
*.pptx
*.xlsx
*.pt
*.pth
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.joblib
*.bin
*.parquet
*.feather
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.sqlite
*.db
*.arrow

